MindForge is an independent AI Dungeon scripting project by Leolynn.

MindForge was inspired by Inner Self by LewdLeah and by common AI Dungeon
scenario scripting patterns around story cards, context modifiers, and output
post-processing. Thank you to Inner Self for the inspiration and for helping
shape the broader NPC-memory scripting style in the AI Dungeon community.

MindForge's implementation is its own runtime: configuration card format,
private-mind prompting, multi-NPC budgeting, memory scoring, invisible labels,
Auto Doctor maintenance, parser repair, quality gates, tests, and release
build scripts are original to this project.
